&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://gist.github.com/sergey-cheperis/530666bc5d7064185ab72bfcaeb19ff1&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
